This topic explains how to install Pivotal Cloud Foundry (PCF) on Microsoft Azure using Terraform.

To install PCF on Azure using Terraform, do the following:

1. Deploy Ops Manager. See [Deploying Ops Manager on Azure Using Terraform](../om/azure/prepare-env-terraform.html).

1. Configure BOSH Director. See [Configuring BOSH Director on Azure Using Terraform](../om/azure/config-terraform.html).

1. Configure PAS. See [Configuring PAS](./configure-pas.html).